T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"夠kong u仔黎就唔駛怕"},{"pid":"2e0367ae927199bc58c2c4fe141d151891d64164","tid":745954,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:06:30.000Z","msg":"Pish 有冇space sci 師兄解答吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075a3c8af72df1d0a25702bf8a9c9da0ba221d99","tid":745954,"uid":195211,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:10:40.000Z","msg":"你好呀<br />\n咁我係SPACE Asso Science Yr 2<br />\n下個學年會入KongU 理學士Yr3<br />\n以下我將會以SPACE Asso Sci既身份闡述看法<br />\n咁的確SPACE入面對比其他科Science入U/UGC機會係高D<br />\n上面的確 Yr2時會有KongU Subject,咁當然要去KongU上<br />\n因為始終係Asso,所以General education會多D<br />\n但會覺得學既時候實用D易上手D<br />\n比如Yr2 要讀既中文科唔會再教你咩閱讀技巧,<br />\n反正會教你同音,異體字果D或者歐化病句,考試只有寫作,認字同改句<br />\n不過呢D都只係過去既例子<br />\n2017年果屈既Yr1開始轉制,改科/cut科,<br />\n詳細你要問翻 3762 2000 (SPACE KEC center) <br />\n同埋如果想真心入KongU/或者好D既UGC<br />\n全部你想讀既主科都盡可能請你A range (PHY/CHEM/BIO)<br />\n祝你兩年後成為成功例子呀"},{"pid":"537121918b158a2c0e838d4fd66b04c62a7d29aa","tid":745954,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"075a3c8af72df1d0a25702bf8a9c9da0ba221d99","tid":745954,"uid":195211,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:10:40.000Z","msg":"你好呀<br />\n咁我係SPACE Asso Science Yr 2<br />\n下個學年會入KongU 理學士Yr3<br />\n以下我將會以SPACE Asso Sci既身份闡述看法<br />\n咁的確SPACE入面對比其他科Science入U/UGC機會係高D<br />\n上面的確 Yr2時會有KongU Subject,咁當然要去KongU上<br />\n因為始終係Asso,所以General education會多D<br />\n但會覺得學既時候實用D易上手D<br />\n比如Yr2 要讀既中文科唔會再教你咩閱讀技巧,<br />\n反正會教你同音,異體字果D或者歐化病句,考試只有寫作,認字同改句<br />\n不過呢D都只係過去既例子<br />\n2017年果屈既Yr1開始轉制,改科/cut科,<br />\n詳細你要問翻 3762 2000 (SPACE KEC center) <br />\n同埋如果想真心入KongU/或者好D既UGC<br />\n全部你想讀既主科都盡可能請你A range (PHY/CHEM/BIO)<br />\n祝你兩年後成為成功例子呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:16:07.000Z","msg":"Thx 師兄<br />\n仲有space 多唔多除咗中英文之外嘅雜科<br />\n仲有要幾高gpa 先升到hku science(難唔難achieve,聽講有好多名校仔屈機）"},{"pid":"954bfdecbbab43aef23e007f998ea10fe6ed6e5a","tid":745954,"uid":89968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4724287d3deda34637c8883cbec844940b531c8","tid":745954,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5bc3bcb766e39855dcec6a6054a26dafcd03ef1","tid":745954,"uid":89968,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4d9645e5a75b6d7425848620db51b0d230be102f","tid":745954,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:41:27.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽講hku space易上hku science但多雜科<br />\nhkcc就師資好啲<br />\n有冇師兄解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:44:09.000Z","msg":"邊個話space師資唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"Space 係咪真係多雜科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"係，讀咩科都多雜科，如philosophy、media、maths，space science有時要去hku上堂，見到個friend讀得幾chur下，兩年後升左上去讀hku science。"},{"pid":"4b6a6fc94a1335374297b46b41bb94728ababf07","tid":745954,"uid":195211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/162804_5a68a7e46eb3cfe9bef871c4d6484aa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F162804_5a68a7e46eb3cfe9bef871c4d6484aa3.jpg&h=468af1c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呢個係手冊中,睇翻Yr1學生的科目,你可以大約睇睇感受下參考下<br />\n<br />\n咁一般而言,如果你sem3的cGPA過3點幾,你去in完之後多數會出Condit俾你<br />\n我就因為sem3未過3,所以in完後佢地話睇翻overall 成績,咁我 sem 4 overall 過3啦,<br />\n咁所有phy主科都A range,所以最後就出Firm offer給我入理學士物理 Yr3<br />\n其他科我唔太清楚,但因為phy少人讀所以上翻去UGC都比較過半<br />\n但bio同chem好多人讀同爭,可能佢地要3.3X ~ 3.5X 以上先入翻KongU? &lt;&lt; This is a general guess only, DO NOT TAKE IT AS A REFERENCE.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過Yr2入U易過Yr1入係好好好真既<br />\n希望有其他師兄出黎話你知啦<br />\n同埋SPACE個office你唔好睇而家打有人聽,過左收生熱潮就好容易打好L多次都冇人聽<br />\n有時打到你起火都仲得<br />\n<br />\n頂我好似真心膠晒成件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c2b49c4ef4a6b6d5375858f5333b07dc855d93","tid":745954,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b6a6fc94a1335374297b46b41bb94728ababf07","tid":745954,"uid":195211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/162804_5a68a7e46eb3cfe9bef871c4d6484aa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F162804_5a68a7e46eb3cfe9bef871c4d6484aa3.jpg&h=468af1c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呢個係手冊中,睇翻Yr1學生的科目,你可以大約睇睇感受下參考下<br />\n<br />\n咁一般而言,如果你sem3的cGPA過3點幾,你去in完之後多數會出Condit俾你<br />\n我就因為sem3未過3,所以in完後佢地話睇翻overall 成績,咁我 sem 4 overall 過3啦,<br />\n咁所有phy主科都A range,所以最後就出Firm offer給我入理學士物理 Yr3<br />\n其他科我唔太清楚,但因為phy少人讀所以上翻去UGC都比較過半<br />\n但bio同chem好多人讀同爭,可能佢地要3.3X ~ 3.5X 以上先入翻KongU? &lt;&lt; This is a general guess only, DO NOT TAKE IT AS A REFERENCE.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過Yr2入U易過Yr1入係好好好真既<br />\n希望有其他師兄出黎話你知啦<br />\n同埋SPACE個office你唔好睇而家打有人聽,過左收生熱潮就好容易打好L多次都冇人聽<br />\n有時打到你起火都仲得<br />\n<br />\n頂我好似真心膠晒成件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f1f8c74f3244e7eef696a3260895d97ef9d604","tid":745954,"uid":134665,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"Hkcc更稱心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214addd527853a00a08719cd535256395c34cd22","tid":745954,"uid":195211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70c2b4